<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
 <title>"required" and the required DOM attribute</title>
 <style>
  input { background:red }
  input:optional { background:lime }
 </style>
 <p>The form control should have a green background: <input required="required"/></p>
 <script> window.onload = function(){ document.getElementsByTagName('input')[0].required = false } </script>
</html>